==发行==
《永远的蝙蝠侠》在发行前作出了几项较大的改动，据导演舒马赫表示，电影原本片长有近160分钟，被删除的镜头包括双面人从精神病院逃出等<ref name=cut>{{cite web | url = http://www.batman-on-film.com/opinion_scissorpuppy_forever.html | title = Batman Forever – What Could Be: A Guide to the Batman Forever Cutting Room Floor | work = Batman-On-Film.com | accessdate = 2013-07-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130702174008/http://www.batman-on-film.com/opinion_scissorpuppy_forever.html | archivedate = 2013-07-02 }}</ref>。

===票房===
《永远的蝙蝠侠》于1995年6月16日在美国的2842家电影院上映，首周进账5278万4433美元<ref name="box" />，这创下了当时电影上映首周的新票房纪录<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=1995&sort=opengross&order=DESC&p=.htm | title = 1995 Domestic Grosses | publisher = Box Office Mojo | accessdate = 2013-07-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130515111110/http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=1995&sort=opengross&order=DESC&p=.htm | archivedate = 2013-05-15 }}</ref>。影片最终在北美收入为1亿8403万1112美元，其他国家入账1亿5249万8032美元，总计3亿3652万9144美元，在商业上获得了成功<ref name="box" />。电影在商业上比前作《蝙蝠侠归来》成功<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/showdowns/chart/?id=batmanvs.htm | title = Batman Battle | work = Box Office Mojo | accessdate = 2013-07-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921074329/http://boxofficemojo.com/showdowns/chart/?id=batmanvs.htm | archivedate = 2013-09-21 }}</ref>，是1995年[[美国本土|美国本土]]的电影票房[[亚军|亚军]]，仅次于《[[玩具总动员|玩具总动员]]》<ref name="dom">{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=releasedate&view=opening&yr=1995&p=.htm |title=1995 Domestic Grosses |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-07-16 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523024352/http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=releasedate&view=opening&yr=1995&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-05-23 }}</ref>。

===专业评价===
《永远的蝙蝠侠》获得的评价褒贬不一。根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上收集的58篇专业评论文章，其中24篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为41%，平均得分5.2（最高10分），网站上对影片的共识评价中写道：“吵吵闹闹，忙个不停，但还是很无聊。不过《永远的蝙蝠侠》还是有[[湯米·李·瓊斯|汤米·李·琼斯]]和[[金·凱瑞|金·凯瑞]]的魅力来救场。”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/batman_forever/ | title = Batman Forever | work = Rotten Tomatoes | publisher = Flixster | accessdate = 2013-07-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130811193353/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/batman_forever/ | archivedate = 2013-08-11 }}</ref>[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]则根据23篇评论文章得出了51的平均分（满分100），其中10篇好评，2篇差评，11篇褒贬不一<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.metacritic.com/movie/batman-forever | title = Batman Forever (1995): Reviews | work = Metacritic | publisher = CBS Interactive | accessdate = 2013-07-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130316015850/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/batman-forever | archivedate = 2013-03-16 }}</ref>。

《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滚石]]》的彼得·特拉维斯（{{lang|en|Peter Travers}}）表示《永远的蝙蝠侠》仍然是优秀的电影，认为该片是这年暑期包括最多惊喜的作品。不过他也批评了影片的过度商品化，觉得剧本中缺乏[[蒂姆·伯顿|蒂姆·伯顿]]给蝙蝠侠创造出的那种长久以前父母被[[谋杀|谋杀]]的痛苦<ref>{{cite news | author = Peter Travers | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/batman-forever-19950616 | title = Batman Forever | work = Rolling Stone | date = 1995-06-16 | accessdate = 2013-07-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140622163718/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/batman-forever-19950616 | archivedate = 2014-06-22 }}</ref>。《[[綜藝|綜藝]]》的布莱恩·洛瑞（{{lang|en|Brian Lowry}}）指出，“有一个需要质疑的是给硬质橡胶制成的蝙蝠衣加上乳头部分的逻辑，这到底是谁的主意？[[阿尔弗莱德·潘尼沃斯|阿尔弗莱德]]？有一些电脑合成的[[高譚市|高谭]]城市景观看上去也太假了。[[艾略特·高登索|艾略特·高登索]]的配乐也不像丹尼·葉夫曼在前两部电影中表现那么轰轰烈烈。”<ref>{{cite news|author=Brian Lowry |url=http://variety.com/1995/film/reviews/batman-forever-1200441944/ |title=Batman Forever |work=Variety |date=1995-07-14 |accessdate=2013-07-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080821175815/http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117904172.html |archivedate=2008-08-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

{{link-en|詹姆斯·伯拉迪尼|James Berardinelli}}称赞影片“更轻松、更明亮、更风趣，节奏也更快，而且比以前（的作品）更加丰富多彩”<ref>{{cite news | author = James Berardinelli | url = http://www.reelviews.net/php_review_template.php?identifier=287 | title = ''Batman Forever'' | work = ReelViews | date = 1995-06-16 | accessdate = 2013-07-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131005005917/http://www.reelviews.net/php_review_template.php?identifier=287 | archivedate = 2013-10-05 }}</ref>。斯科特·比提感觉“汤米·李·琼斯把哈维·登特当成[[小丑_(漫畫)|小丑]]在演，而不是一个多层次的无赖”<ref>{{cite news | author = Bill "Jett" Ramey | url = http://batman-on-film.com/sbeattyinterview.html | title = BOF Interview: Scott Beatty | work = Batman-on-Film | date = 2005-11-28 | accessdate = 2013-07-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20110707193850/http://batman-on-film.com/sbeattyinterview.html | archivedate = 2011-07-07 }}</ref>。李·伯米乔（{{lang|en|Lee Bermejo}}）称《永远的蝙蝠侠》让人“不堪忍受”<ref>{{cite news |author=Bill "Jett" Ramey |url=http://batman-on-film.com/leebermejointerview.html |title=Interview: Lee Bermejo |work=Batman-on-Film |date=2005-10-13 |accessdate=2013-07-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080915114140/http://www.batman-on-film.com/leebermejointerview.html |archivedate=2008-09-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的[[罗杰·艾伯特|罗杰·艾伯特]]给予本片两星半的评价（最高四星），他在自己的评论中写道：“这部电影是不是更有娱乐性？好吧，对于小孩子们来说，这片子会比较容易消化。想想《蝙蝠侠归来》曾导致一些孩子们嚎啕大哭，那個什么[[美国电影分级制度|PG-13级]]可真是个笑话。”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/batman-forever-1995 |title=Batman Forever |author=Roger Ebert |publisher=rogerebert.com |accessdate=2008-08-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080722031139/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F19950616%2FREVIEWS%2F506160301%2F1023 |archivedate=2008-07-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>米克·拉萨尔（{{lang|en|Mick LaSalle}}）评价上褒贬不一，认为“给基默的橡胶（蝙蝠）衣上来一枪保证可以引来观众的尖叫声”<ref>{{cite news|author=Mick LaSalle |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/1995/06/16/DD8003.DTL |title=''Batman Forever'' Goes On and On |work=San Francisco Chronicle |date=1995-06-16 |accessdate=2008-08-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080921093641/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F1995%2F06%2F16%2FDD8003.DTL |archivedate=2008-09-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

===奖项===
在[[第68届奥斯卡金像奖|第68届奥斯卡金像奖]]角逐中，《永远的蝙蝠侠》获得了[[奥斯卡最佳摄影奖|摄影]]、[[奥斯卡最佳音效奖|音效]]和[[奥斯卡最佳音效剪辑奖|音效剪辑]]3项提名，不过都没能获奖，分别败给了《[[勇敢的心|勇敢的心]]》和《[[阿波罗13号_(电影)|阿波罗13号]]》。<ref name="Oscars1996">{{cite web|url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/68th-winners.html |title=The 68th Academy Awards (1996) Nominees and Winners |work=oscars.org |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014180250/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/68th-winners.html |archivedate=2013-10-14 }}</ref>由[[U2乐团|U2乐团]]表演的歌曲《{{lang|en|Hold Me, Thrill Me, Kiss Me, Kill Me}}》获得了[[金球奖|金球奖]]最佳原创歌曲奖提名，但不敌《[[風中奇緣_(電影)|风中奇缘]]》的《{{lang|en|Colors of the Wind}}》。<ref name="GoldenGlobe1995">{{Cite news |url=http://www.goldenglobes.org/browse/?param=/year/1995 |title=The 53rd Annual Golden Globe Awards (1996) |language=en |work=goldenglobes.org |accessdate=2013-07-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130521171216/http://www.goldenglobes.org/browse/?param=%2Fyear%2F1995 |archivedate=2013-05-21 }}</ref>另外这首歌也被提名[[金酸莓奖|金酸莓奖]]最差原创歌曲，还好也没有获奖。影片还获得[[土星奖|土星奖]]最佳奇幻电影、化妆、特技效果、服装设计提名，为电影谱曲的艾略特·戈登塞尔获得了一奖[[格莱美奖|格莱美奖]]提名。此外还有[[MTV电影大奖|MTV电影大奖]]、[[儿童选择奖|儿童选择奖]]等多个奖项提名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0112462/awards |title=Awards for Batman Forever (1995) |work=IMDb |accessdate=2013-07-16 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130403062438/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0112462/awards |archivedate=2013-04-03 }}</ref>。

